Wmns Five Ten Freerider Pro 'Hazy Emerald'
results.story: The adidas women’s Five Ten Freerider Pro ‘Hazy Emerald’ highlights a monochromatic color scheme on a flat-pedal mountain biking shoe built for all-day comfort. The quick-drying synthetic upper is enhanced with a perforated toe box for added breathability and textured urethane overlays at the toe and heel for abrasion-resistant durability. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a molded EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a Stealth S1 rubber outsole with a Dotty rubber tread for superior pedal control.

results.name: Wmns Fresh Foam Tempo 2E Wide 'Light Blue'
Wmns Fresh Foam Tempo 2E Wide 'Vivid Coral'
Wmns Five Ten Freerider 'Wild Teal'
results.story: The adidas women’s Five Ten Freerider ‘Wild Teal’ delivers a mountain biking shoe that blends performance-driven details with casual style. The upper is constructed from breathable green mesh with tonal suede overlays and a grey synthetic leather heel wrap. Both numerals are integrated into the Five Ten logo that adorns the lateral quarter panel, while a woven Freerider tag is affixed to the collar. Underfoot, the outsole features Stealth S1 rubber construction with a Dotty tread.

results.name: Ken Scott x Gucci Wmns Ace 'Floral'
Wmns Zig Kinetica 2 'Chalk Orange Flare'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Zig Kinetica 2 ‘Chalk Orange Flare’ combines breathable comfort with responsive cushioning that adds spring to every stride. An off-white tone suffuses the mesh upper, reinforced with a series of tonal wavy overlays and contrasted by subtle orange coloring that peeks through the quarter panels. The lifestyle runner rides on a Floatride Fuel midsole, encased in a Zig Energy Shell and supported underfoot by an outsole with Zig Energy Bands that snap back for enhanced energy return.

results.name: adidas Forum Mid Ivy Park Icy Park Cream White (W)
results.story: The Ivy Park x adidas Forum Mid ‘Cream White’ is taken from the ‘Icy Park’ collection, developed in partnership with Beyonce’s streetwear brand and featuring a wintry Alpine theme. The vintage hoops shoe is updated with a premium leather and suede build in neutral white and cream tones. An adjustable strap wraps around the collar, featuring a padded interior lined in soft terry cloth for a comfortable fit. The mid-top is mounted on a rubber midsole, enhanced with an EVA wedge and supported by a gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Ivy Park x Wmns Super Sleek Boot 'Icy Park'
results.story: Launching as part of an Alpine-themed collection with Beyonce’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas women’s Super Sleek Boot ‘Icy Park’ features a high-cut collar on a premium leather and suede upper. Metal hardware and an elastic bungee cord wrapped around the heel add to the sneaker-boot’s mountaineering aesthetic. The towering silhouette is mounted on an exaggerated gum rubber sole unit, featuring a herringbone traction pattern for reliable grip.

results.name: Wmns Club MEMT 'White Gum'
results.story: The Reebok women’s Club MEMT ‘White Gum’ steps out in an ultra-clean design, featuring a layered leather upper entirely devoid of color. Tonal Reebok branding adorns the woven tongue tag and lateral-side logo window. A comfortable terry cloth lining nods to the sneaker’s tennis-inspired design theme, while a removable EVA sockliner offers lightweight cushioning. Underfoot, a gum rubber outsole delivers grippy traction and the shoe’s lone pop of contrasting color.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost Ivy Park Icy Park (W)
results.story: The Ivy Park x adidas UltraBoost 4.0 ‘Ivy Park’ gives the responsive running shoe an alabaster makeover, courtesy of Beyonce’s athleisure brand. White Primeknit makes up the breathable composition of the upper, secured with drawcord lacing and an off-white midfoot cage. The same neutral hue is applied to the molded heel counter, featuring embossed Ivy Park branding on the lateral side. The lightweight build is mounted on a Boost midsole, supported by a Continental gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Jordan 1 Low SE Black Metallic Silver (W)
adidas Sleek Boot Ivy Park Icy Park (W)
Ivy Park x Wmns Sleek Boot 'Icy Park'
results.story: Launching as part of a larger collection with Beyonce’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas women’s Sleek Boot ‘Icy Park’ blends streetwear style with alpine-ready details. The retro-inspired sneaker-boot hybrid features a premium blend of white leather and tonal suede on the quarter panel, tongue and collar. Speed hooks and D-ring eyelets are integrated into the lacing system, while a bungee cord around the heel allows the shoe to be clipped onto a backpack or bag. The gum rubber platform sole features a herringbone traction pattern for superior grip.

results.name: adidas Supersleek 72 Ivy Park Icy Park (W)
results.story: Launching as part of an Alpine-themed collection with Beyonce’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas women’s Super Sleek 72 ‘Icy Park’ features an exaggerated double-stacked midsole in a pristine white finish. The sneaker’s platform tooling is countered by a low-profile upper, constructed from white leather with off-white suede overlays that include the Samba’s signature T-toe. An integrated lacing system includes bungee detailing wrapped around the heel, allowing the shoe to be clipped onto a carryall.

results.name: Ken Scott x Gucci Wmns Screener 'Floral'
adidas Forum Mid Ivy Park Icy Park Silver (W)
results.story: The Ivy Park x adidas Forum Mid ‘Silver Metallic’ is drawn from the ‘Icy Park’ collection, an alpine-themed joint venture developed in partnership with Beyonce’s athleisure brand. This refreshed take on the vintage hoops shoe features a reflective metallic silver finish throughout leather upper, secured with an integrated lacing system and an adjustable ankle strap. The mid-top rests on a grey rubber midsole, enhanced with an EVA wedge and reinforced by a tacky gum rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Five Ten Trailcross LT 'Legacy Green'
results.story: The adidas women’s Five Ten Trailcross LT ‘Legacy Green’ delivers a versatile low-top that can be used for mountain biking or hiking. A military khaki hue is executed on the mesh and synthetic upper, accented with Five Ten branding in Signal Coral. An open mesh tongue provides added breathability, while binding around the low-cut collar offers abrasion-free comfort. The sneaker sits atop a lightweight EVA midsole, supported underfoot by a Stealth Phantom Dotty rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Basket Classic 21 'White Byzantium'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Basket Classic 21 ‘White Byzantium’ revives the 1971 hoops shoe with a lightly refreshed build and vibrant bursts of color. They take the form of magenta accents on the heel tab and stitched Formstrip, allowing the details to stand out against a stark white leather backdrop. Additionally, ‘PUMA Basket’ shines in metallic gold print on the lateral quarter panel. Underfoot, a non-marking rubber outsole delivers multi-directional traction.

results.name: Wmns Basket Classic 21 'White Nimbus Cloud'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Basket Classic 21 ‘White Nimbus Cloud’ applies a monochromatic finish to a low-top silhouette drawn from the brand’s 1970s archive. Lightly refreshed for the 21st century, the vintage hoops shoe makes use of a white leather upper, accented with a stitched leather Formstrip in a subtle off-white shade. The monotone palette is disrupted by a woven PUMA tongue tag and metallic gold branding hits at the heel and lateral quarter panel.

results.name: Nike Dunk Low Coast (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Dunk Low ‘Coast’ highlights traditional two-tone color blocking on a leather upper that maintains the look of the original 1985 release. A crisp white base, replete with perforated detailing on the toe box, is contrasted by overlays in a vibrant blue finish. Nike branding on the heel tab and woven tongue tag are rendered in an unexpected pop of yellow. The sneaker rides on a low-profile midsole, supported by a rubber outsole featuring concentric circle tread.

results.name: Wmns DailyFit 'Vector Navy'
results.story: The Reebok women’s DailyFit ‘Vector Navy’ delivers a monochromatic colorway of a lightweight, versatile walking shoe. The slip-on textile upper features faux decorative laces and a molded heel designed to cradle the back of the foot. Flexible cushioning arrives via a full-length, segmented foam midsole. Underfoot, Reebok’s DMX moving air technology is visible through the translucent rubber outsole, etched with a wavy traction pattern for optimal grip.

results.name: Wmns Cruise Rider 'Pink Lady Yellow Pear'
Wmns Basket Classic 21 'Triple White'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Basket Classic 21 ‘Triple White’ makes over the classic low-top with refreshed details and a clean, monochromatic finish. The minimalist leather upper is bereft of almost all color, save for metallic gold branding elements at the heel and lateral quarter panel. Perforated detailing on the sneaker’s side panels delivers improved breathability, while PUMA’s comfort sockliner provides lightweight cushioning with each step.

results.name: Wmns Novablast 'Pixel Noise - French Blue Champagne'
Wmns Basket Classic 21 'White Black'
results.story: The PUMA women’s Basket Classic 21 ‘White Black’ showcases an essential two-tone palette on a lightly refreshed iteration of the vintage hoops shoe. The low-top makes use of a crisp white leather upper, accented with a contrasting black Formstrip and gold-foil PUMA Basket branding. The brand’s jumping cat logo adorns the heel tab in the same gilded finish. Underfoot, the non-marking rubber outsole features a grid-like tread originally designed for the hardwood.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Move Low 'Light Field Surplus'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star Move Low ‘Light Field Surplus’ gives the iconic silhouette a bold makeover, highlighted by a molded platform sole unit that adds height but not excess weight. Up top, traditional canvas construction is finished in a pale green hue and lined in 100% recycled mesh for improved breathability. A reinforced rubber toe cap maintains the classic Chuck Taylor aesthetic, while an Ortholite sockliner provides step-in comfort.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star High 'It's Okay To Wander'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘It's Okay to Wander’ features embroidered details on an off-white canvas upper. The nature-inspired graphics — spanning the moon, the sun, a river and flowers — connects with a hidden message on the interior tongue that states ‘It’s okay to wander from yourself to the world.’ The high-top is finished with signature Chuck Taylor touches, including a circular All Star ankle patch, chrome eyelets and a reinforced rubber toe cap.

results.name: Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star Platform High 'It's Okay To Wander - Egret'
Wmns DailyFit 'Black'
results.story: The Reebok women’s DailyFit ‘Black’ treats the lightweight walking shoe to a subdued, monotone finish. Faux decorative laces are integrated into the black textile upper, featuring a bound collar and a molded heel designed to cradle the back of the foot. The slip-on silhouette is mounted on a segmented foam midsole for a smooth and flexible ride. Underfoot, Reebok’s moving air DMX cushioning is visible beneath the translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Wmns Sleek Super 'Leopard'
results.story: The adidas women’s Sleek Super ‘Leopard’ outfits the lifestyle silhouette with audacious details intended to make a statement. An oversized Trefoil lace jewel shines in metallic gold, nearly stealing the spotlight from the leopard print that covers virtually every inch of the leather upper. The all-over design is interrupted by a tan suede heel tab and an adidas logo window on the lateral eyestay. An exaggerated platform midsole anchors the streamlined upper.
